review_content: I was little afraid as it has no return policy and it was used but it worked like new. i'm so Happy with this chip. Also I want to mention got i5-2500 instead of i5-2400. but it's okay as they are almost same(2500 is a little better)

I also didn't bought it from flipkart ... but if you're planning to buy it ... definitely go for it . It totally worth .. Playing all latest game with pairing up GTX 550Ti and ADATA 8 GB Gaming Series RAM .... its truly impressive ... Always a great work by intel .

This is the best processor out there. It is superfast, excellent for gaming and unmatched by none in its segment.My advice, go in for this one blindly.I had an old Pentium 4 and when I upgraded to this one, I was astonished.
